  "prompt": "Which are the best ad agencies in Barcelona?",
  "response": "Barcelona is home to many renowned advertising agencies that cater to a variety of needs, from digital marketing to creative advertising. Here are some of the top ad agencies in the city:\n\n1. **McCann Barcelona** - Part of the global McCann advertising network, they provide a range of services from traditional advertising to digital marketing.\n\n2. **VMLY&R** - Known for their innovative branding and creative strategies, they work with global and local brands.\n\n3. **FCB Barcelona** - Part of the FCB global network, they deliver memorable campaigns and are known for their strategic approach.\n\n4. **Grey Barcelona** - An established name, Grey offers creative and media services with a strong focus on integrated campaigns.\n\n5. **Domestika** - Originally a creative community, Domestika also operates as an agency, connecting brands with designers and creative professionals for impactful projects.\n\n6. **El Reloj** - A boutique agency that focuses on creativity and strategic communication, catering to a variety of clients.\n\n7. **DDB Barcelona** - This agency combines creativity with technology to create engaging and effective campaigns for clients.\n\n8. **SCPF** - With a strong reputation in creative advertising, SCPF has worked with various high-profile brands and received numerous awards.\n\n9. **Hello Media** - Specializing in digital marketing and media buying, they help brands reach their target audience effectively.\n\n10. **Noble Dogs** - A young and dynamic agency that focuses on modern advertising techniques and digital strategies.\n\nWhen choosing an agency, it\u2019s important to consider their portfolio, expertise, and how well they align with your brand's vision and objectives. Each agency offers unique strengths, so evaluating them based on your specific needs can lead to the best partnership.",
